### PUT /api/medicos/:id — Actualizar un médico
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/medicos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Dr. Francisco Actualizado",
  "especialidad": "Cardiología Intervencionista"
}


### PUT /api/medicos/:id — NOT FOUND (404)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/medicos/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "No existe",
  "especialidad": "Ninguna"
}


### DELETE /api/medicos/:id — Eliminar un médico
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/medicos/1


### DELETE /api/medicos/:id — NOT FOUND (404)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/medicos/999